        {
            "title": "美國政府接近達成5億美元Spirit救助方案 或持有高達90%股份",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 知情人士稱透露，川普政府接近達成一項針對Spirit Airlines的救助方案，該方案可能賦予美國政府一項選擇權，使其在該航空公司走出破產程序後可持有多達90%的股份。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些在交易宣布前要求匿名的知情人士表示，該協議尚未最終敲定，擬提供最高5億美元融資，以換取可購買新實體最多90%股權的認股權證。談判仍存變數，也有可能無法達成協議。目前尚不清楚美國政府最終會持有多少股份。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國總統唐納德·川普周二表示，他願意考慮向這家航空公司提供聯邦援助。知情人士稱，美國商務部長霍華德·盧特尼克正牽頭推動這一潛在的政府方案。其中一位知情人士表示，政府內部對於是否推進該計畫仍存在分歧。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2f73b580-cab9-3149-aba8-5d7e4a93c82c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在政府可能出手救助、從而幫助其避免被清算的預期推動下，Spirit Aviation Holdings Inc.股價一度飆升57%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">《華爾街日報》率先報導稱川普政府接近就Spirit達成協議。彭博此前報導，由於美國與以色列對伊朗開戰推升航空燃油價格，Spirit面臨潛在清算風險，該公司曾提出由政府入股的設想，尋求緊急救助。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Could Own Up to 90% of Spirit as Part of $500 Million Rescue</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Jennifer A Dlouhy.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">(首段起新增更多救助方案細節)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%8E%A5%E8%BF%91%E6%95%B2%E5%AE%9A5%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83spirit%E6%95%91%E5%8A%A9%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88-145921024.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-23 01:16:19",
